[30;1m20 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35mWhen you install coverage.py, a command-line script called ``coverage`` is[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35mplaced on your path.  To help with multi-version installs, it will also create[0m
